        <div class="section">
            <h2>What is this bot?</h2>
            <p>
                <code>CytherAI-AnimationBot</code> is a research web crawler operated by CytherAI.
                It collects publicly available anime character images and animation references
                for training a <strong class="highlight">Character-Centric Animation Network (CCAN)</strong> —
                an AI model that generates consistent character animations from reference images.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2>User-Agent String</h2>
            <pre class="code-block">CytherAI-AnimationBot/1.0 (+https://cytherai.com/bots/ccan; contact: Aethdev@cytherai.com)</pre>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Crawling Behavior</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Respects robots.txt</strong> — We honor all directives in your robots.txt file</li>
                <li><strong>Rate limited</strong> — Maximum 1 request per 3 seconds per domain</li>
                <li><strong>Low volume</strong> — Typically &lt;1000 images per character tag</li>
                <li><strong>API-first</strong> — Uses official APIs when available (Danbooru, Gelbooru)</li>
                <li><strong>Caches responses</strong> — We don't re-request content unnecessarily</li>
                <li><strong>Identifies itself</strong> — Always sends the User-Agent string above</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2>What We Collect</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Character reference images (single character, clear poses)</li>
                <li>Expression sheets and character turnarounds</li>
                <li>Animation keyframes from sakugabooru (credited animators)</li>
                <li>Publicly tagged metadata (character names, pose tags, expression tags)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                We do <strong class="warning-text">not</strong> collect: personal data, login-protected content,
                images marked as "do not repost", NSFW content, or any content from artists who have
                opted out of AI training.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2>Artist Opt-Out</h2>
            <p>
                We respect artist wishes. If you are an artist and want your work excluded:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:optout@cytherai.com">optout@cytherai.com</a> with your artist tag/name</li>
                <li>We maintain an exclusion list and will remove any cached content within 48 hours</li>
                <li>We also honor the <code>ai:no</code> and <code>do_not_train</code> tags on imageboards</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <h2>How to Block This Bot</h2>
            <p>Add the following to your <code>robots.txt</code> file:</p>
            <pre class="code-block">User-agent: CytherAI-AnimationBot
Disallow: /</pre>
            <p>Or to block specific directories:</p>
            <pre class="code-block">User-agent: CytherAI-AnimationBot
Disallow: /gallery/
Disallow: /private/</pre>
        </div>
        
        <div class="contact-section">
